high_descs: Turn right move forward then turn left on the side table
Pick up the pen on the table
Put the pen in the mug
Pick up the mug with pen on the table
Turn left walk straight then head to the tv stand
Put the mug with pen on the tv stand
anns.task_desc: Put mug with pen on the tv stand

high_descs: Turn to the right and step forward. Face the side table with the lamp on it.
Pick up the pen from the side table.
Place the pen inside the mug on the side table.
Pick up the mug with the pen.
Turn left and go forward. Walk over to the tv stand and turn to the right to face it.
Place the mug on the tv stand by the left corner of it.
anns.task_desc: Move the pen and mug to the tv stand.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the circular table ini the corner.
Place black pencil in the white mug.
Turn left and walk to the TV stand, then face it.
Place the mug on the TV stand, just in front of the TV on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a pen in it on a TV stand.
